../README.md:425:## txtstore
../README.md:427:`txtstore` is a sectioned markdown file store for waveplan artifacts (implementation notes, review notes, etc.). It uses an MCP server architecture: `txtstore-mcp` (Go MCP server) + `txtstore` (Go CLI proxy).
